holster |1987|p=91}}|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=o3INAQAAIAAJ | title=Paarl Valley, 1687\u20131987 | year=1987 | isbn=0-7969-0539-8 |last1=Oberholster |first1=A. G. |last2=Van Breda |first2=Pieter |  publisher=Human Sciences Research Council}}\n*{{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Thomas Pakenham|1992}}|last=Pakenham|first=Thomas|title=Boer War|url= https://books.google.com/books?id=JjEPngEACAAJ|year=1992|publisher=HarperCollins|isbn=9780380720019}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Parsons|1993}}|last=Parsons|first=Neil |title=A New History of Southern Africa|url=https://archive.org/details/newhistoryofsout0000pars|url-access=registration|year=1993|publisher=Macmillan|location=London|isbn=978-0-8419-5319-2}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Phelan|1913}}|last=Phelan|first=T. |title=The Siege of Kimberley|url=http://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/13777|year=1913|publisher=M.H. Gill and Son|location=Dublin|isbn=978-0-554-24773-1}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Picton-Seymour|1989}}|last=Picton-Seymour|first=D\u00e9sir\u00e9e |title=Historical Buildings in South Africa|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Pg1QAAAAMAAJ|year=1989|publisher=Struikhof Publishers|isbn=978-0-947458-01-0}}\n*{{cite book|first=Thomas|last= Pinney|ref=harv|title=The Letters of Rudyard Kipling: Volume 3: 1900\u201310|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uC6wCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA72|year=1995|publisher=Palgrave Macmillan UK|page=72|isbn=9781349137398}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Plomer|1984}}|last=Plomer|first=William |title=Cecil Rhodes|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BYwingEACAAJ|year=1984|publisher=D. Philip|isbn=978-0-08646018-9}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Radziwill|1918}} |last=Radziwill|first=Princess Catherine |title=Cecil Rhodes: Man and Empire Maker|url=http://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/16600|date=1918 |publisher= CASSELL & COMPANY, LTD |location=London, New York, Toronto and Melbourne |isbn=978-0-554-35300-5}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Rhodes|1902}}|last=Rhodes|first=Cecil |editor=Stead, William Thomas