ks?id=uzdzQgAACAAJ|year=1997|publisher=St. Martin's Press|isbn=978-0-312-16982-4}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Thompson|2007}}|last=Thompson|first=J. Lee |title=Forgotten Patriot: A Life of Alfred, Viscount Milner of St. James's and Cape Town, 1854-1925|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=PDMcYymUie8C&pg=PA131|year=2007|publisher=Fairleigh Dickinson Univ Press|isbn=978-0-8386-4121-7}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Twain|1898}}|last=Twain|first=Mark|title=A Journey around the World|url=http://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/2895|year=1898|publisher=The American Publishing Company|location=Hartford, CT}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Williams|1921}}|last=Williams|first=Basil |title=Cecil Rhodes|url=https://archive.org/details/cecilrhodes00will|year=1921|publisher=Holt}}\n*{{cite book|ref=harv|last=Wilson|first=Scott |title=Resting Places: The Burial Sites of More Than 14,000 Famous Persons, 3d ed.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FOHgDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA848|date=16 September 2016|publisher=McFarland|isbn=978-1-4766-2599-7}}\n\n=== Encyclopedia ===\n* {{cite book |ref={{sfnref|Domville-Fife|1900 |p=89}}|last=Domville-Fife |first=C.W. |title=The encyclopedia of the British Empire the first encyclopedic record of the greatest empire in the history of the world |year=1900 |publisher=Rankin |location=Bristol |page=89 |url=https://archive.org/stream/encyclopediaofbr01domvuoft#page/88/mode/2up}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Farwell|2001}}|last=Farwell|first=Byron |title=The Encyclopedia of Nineteenth-century Land Warfare: An Illustrated World View|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=m-XpP_pdANcC&pg=PA539|year=2001|publisher=W. W. Norton & Company|isbn=978-0-393-04770-7}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{sfnref|Panton|2015}}|last=Panton|first=Kenneth J. |title=Historical Dictionary of the British Empire|year=2015|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|location=London|isbn=978-0810878013}}\n\n=== Journal articles ===\n* {{cite journal | last =  Brown | first = Richard | date = November 1990 | title = The 